{"query":"mutation AddTableColumnOption($input: AddTableColumnOptionInput!) {
  addColumnOption(input: $input) {
    _id
		type
		field
		dateType
		valueType
		label
    options {
      _id
			order
			label
			color
			system
			statusGroup
			createdAt
			updatedAt
    }
		format
		width
		minWidth
		system
		hidden
		fixed
		resizable
		order
		createdAt
		updatedAt
		table
    __typename
  }
}","operationName":"AddTableColumnOption","variables":"{
	"input": {
		"tableId": "6619735d83a7b01b97fc9172",
		"columnId": "6622ba02a35cac385d26ec97",
		"optionData": {
			"label": "new label",
			"color": "green",
			"order": 1,
			"system": true,
			"statusGroup": "IN_PROGRESS"
		}
	}
}"}

{"query":"mutation CreateTableColumn($input: CreateTableColumnInput!) {
  createColumn(input: $input) {
    _id
		type
		field
		dateType
		valueType
		label
    options {
      _id
			order
			label
			color
			system
			statusGroup
			createdAt
			updatedAt
    }
		format
		width
		minWidth
		system
		hidden
		fixed
		resizable
		order
		createdAt
		updatedAt
		table
    __typename
  }
}","operationName":"CreateTableColumn","variables":"{
	"input": {
		"table": "6619735d83a7b01b97fc9172",
		"type": "DATE",
		"description": "description test",
		"field": "field test",
		"dateType": "dateType test",
		"fieldType": "STRING",
		"label": "Label test",
		"valueType": "DATE",
		"options": [
			{
				"label": "label test",
				"color": "red",
				"order": 1
			}
		]
	}
}"}
